1. *Ono* je dobro. (It is good.)
2. Njemu je *ono* bilo čudno. (That was strange to him.)
3. *Ono* je bilo još čudnije. (That was even stranger.)
4. Nisu mu verovali ono što je rekao. (They didn't believe what he said.)
5. *Ono* je bilo nešto što niko nije očekivao. (That was something nobody expected.)